Installation:
	1) Install all the required libraries (QT and opengl).
	2) Move to src directory (>>cd [path-to-src])
	3) Compile (>>make all)
	4) Run (>>./TextureMapping <path-to-ply-file-1> <path-to-ply-file-2>)

User Interaction options:

	ZOOM-IN/OUT  				----- GUI Slider
	ROTATE   						----- Mouse Left key + drag
	Translate						----- GUI Slider
	Toggle Lights 			----- GUI checkbox
	Toggle Bounding Box ----- GUI checkbox
	Toggle Texture 			----- GUI checkbox
	Change Texture 			----- GUI push button
	Exit          			----- esc
	

Program Features:

	1) Entire program is built using MVC architecture.
	2) A graphical user interface is provided for easy user interaction using QT.
	3) The program can handle any given .ply files and textures once files are named accordingly.

